  "prompt": "What do Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra do?",
  "response": "Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra provide a wide range of technology services and solutions to businesses globally. Their key services include:\n\n1. Information Technology Services:\n- Software development\n- Application maintenance\n- Cloud computing solutions\n- IT infrastructure management\n- Digital transformation consulting\n\n2. Business Process Outsourcing (BPO):\n- Customer support\n- Finance and accounting services\n- Human resources management\n- Data processing\n\n3. Consulting Services:\n- Digital strategy consulting\n- Technology implementation\n- Enterprise architecture\n- Cybersecurity solutions\n\n4. Industry-specific Solutions:\n- Banking and financial services\n- Healthcare\n- Manufacturing\n- Telecommunications\n- Retail\n\n5. Emerging Technologies:\n- Artificial Intelligence\n- Machine Learning\n- Robotic Process Automation\n- Internet of Things (IoT)\n- Blockchain solutions\n\nThese companies primarily serve clients in North America, Europe, and other global markets, offering cost-effective and high-quality technology services. They act as technology partners helping businesses modernize their operations, develop software, and implement advanced technological solutions.\n\nMost of their workforce is based in India, but they also have offices and employees in multiple countries worldwide.",
